high_descs: Turn left then turn right and move forward to the brown table.
Pick up the table knife from the brown table.
Turn right then left and move forward to the microwave.
Open the microwave, slice the apple in the microwave, close microwave.
Take table knife, turn right, then right again then left towards the fridge.
Open fridge door, place knife on shelf inside the fridge, close fridge door.
Turn left, then left again then right towards the microwave.
Open microwave, take out sliced apple from microwave, close microwave.
Take sliced apple, turn right , then right again then left towards the fridge.
Open fridge, place sliced apple next to table knife on the shelf inside the fridge, close fridge door.
Open fridge door, take out sliced apple, turn around and move forward towards the brown table.
Place sliced apple onto brown table next to the tomato
anns.task_desc: Slice an apple take it to the fridge and serve the sliced apple on the table.

high_descs: Turn left then face the table in front of you.
Take the knife off of the table in front of you.
Turn right and face the microwave in front of you.
Slice the apple in the microwave and close it.
Turn right and face the fridge to your left.
Place the knife in the fridge in front of you and close it.
Turn around and face the microwave to your right.
Take an apple slice out of the microwave in front of you and close it.
Turn right and face the fridge to your left.
Place the apple in the fridge in front of you then take it out.
Turn around and face the table in front of you.
Place the apple slice on the table in front of you.
anns.task_desc: Place a cold apple slice on the table.

high_descs: Go to the table past the door on the left.
Pick up the butter knife in the center of the table.
Go to the microwave.
Slice the apple in the microwave.
Go across the room to the fridge.
Put the butter knife in the fridge.
Turn around and go back to the microwave.
Pick up an apple slice from the microwave.
Take the slice to the fridge.
Cool off the apple slice in the fridge.
Take the cooled apple slice to the table across the room.
Set the apple slice down on the table in front of the tomato.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled apple slice on the table.
